modelIdentification.name: JLVC-Base
modelIdentification.purpose: Uses aggregation to add JLVC unique attributes to RPR-FOM objects.

objectClass.name: UniqueEntity
objectClass.semantics: Adds data required by the Order-of-Battle Service (OBS). Entites can not participate in JLVC scenarios without this information.

attribute.name: LVCID
attribute.semantics: An unique identifier specified by the OBS xml file. Entites can not participate in JLVC scenarios without this information.

attribute.name: SideName
attribute.semantics: An optional attribute specifing the side to which the object instance belongs.

attribute.name: MySuperior
attribute.semantics: An optional reference to the LVCID of this object's superior.

objectClass.name: JLVCEntity
objectClass.semantics: A set of optional attributes added in JLVC to provide additional detail to RPR FOM objects.

attribute.name: AlternateForceIdentifier
attribute.semantics: The identification of the force that the entity is disguised as. A value of Other is used to indicate the entity is not in disguise and the AlternateEntityType attribute is meaningless.

attribute.name: BehaviorControlStatus
attribute.semantics: Control states for specific items related to behavior models.

attribute.name: EmitterStatus
attribute.semantics: Indicates this platform is emitting an RF emission.

attribute.name: FiringStatus
attribute.semantics: Active state of gunfire typically used to trigger visual gunfire animations.

attribute.name: isTowed
attribute.semantics: Indicates whether the object instance is being towed (true) or not (false)

attribute.name: LiveVirtualConstructive
attribute.semantics: Attribute type which indicates what type of federate is generating the entity, Live (Instrumented air, ground or sea), Virtual (manned cockpit simulators) or Constructive Simulation

attribute.name: Publisher
attribute.semantics: Value indentifies the particular federate that is currently publishing this entity.

objectClass.name: CBRNEntity
objectClass.semantics: The posture of the object for chemical, biological, radiological, and nuclear (CBRN) effects.

attribute.name: CBRNEffectLowRes
attribute.semantics: Specifies the MOPP level and suit parameters of this entity.

simpleData.name: Angle_Degree_North_Float32
simpleData.semantics: Number of degrees measured clockwise from True North

enumeratedData.name: LiveVirtualConstructiveEnum8
enumeratedData.semantics: indicates whether the object is owned by a live, virtual, or constructive federate.

enumeratedData.name: RPRboolean
enumeratedData.semantics: Standard boolean type used for 8-bit compatibility

enumeratedData.name: EnableDisableEnum8
enumeratedData.semantics: indicates whether the object is enabled or disabled

arrayData.name: LVCIDStruct
arrayData.semantics: String of characters represented by an 11 element character string.

fixedRecordData.name: BehaviorControlStatusStruct
fixedRecordData.semantics: Contains data relative to controlling CGF behavioral models.

field.name: LGWControl
field.semantics: Controls weapon delivery options for CGF laser guided weapons. When buddy lasing is enabled, the LGW are coded with the associated code and third party lasing is expected.

field.name: SkillLevel
field.semantics: Used to control assigned skill level for CGF behavioral models.

field.name: Expenables
field.semantics: Used to disable or enable the ability to dispense expendables. Enabling does not initiate dispensing just the ability to dispense.

field.name: Radar
field.semantics: Used to disable or enable the ability to employ Radar. Enabling does not initiate Radar just the ability to use Radar.

field.name: RFJammer
field.semantics: Used to disable or enable the ability to employ an RF Jammer. Enabling does not initiate jamming just the ability to jam

field.name: Weapons
field.semantics: Used to disable or enable the ability to fire / launch weapons. Enabling does not initiate firing just the ability to fire

field.name: Bearing
field.semantics: Bearing measured in degrees from True North

field.name: ContamDetected
field.semantics: indicates whether contamination is detected (true) or not

fixedRecordData.name: LGWControlStruct
fixedRecordData.semantics: Contains data necessary to control behavior of CGF player when employing laser guided weapons using buddy lasing

field.name: BuddyLase
field.semantics: Identifies if buddy lasing is expected during laser guided weapon deliveries

field.name: BuddyLaseCode
field.semantics: The laser code to be employed by buddy lasing player.
